title: The Donkey of the Day ( Everyone That Got Fake PPP Loans)

description:
Charlamagne gives "Donkey of the Day" to everyone that used fake PPP Loans, after President Joe Biden announces he is signing 2 bipartisan bills, that will give the federal and local prosecutors to have more time to hold criminals accountable for defrauding the American people.
